ding medding medding if i solo.  Course if you got a good book it ain't that bad =P hope this helps.<br>
<br>
btw, i never used earth hardly to solo at all either.  I found its root never worked very well at all in my xp.  I do use it now though at 45 in the DL to solo  for some reason it sticks drolvargs to the ground like glue.  in groups though i whipout the44 airpet to outdamage the tank and stun the mobs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
